<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
  <title>Cover summary | MyService</title>
  <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
  <noscript><p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p></noscript>
  <nav class="uikit-skip-link"><a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a></nav>
  <% include ../../../global/partials/header-version.ejs %>
  <% include ../../header-authenticated.ejs %>
  <% include ../partials/help-button.ejs %>
  <main>
    <section>
      <div class="container" id="main-content">

    	<% include ../partials/progress-bar.ejs %>
        <h1>Add cover - review and submit</h1>
        <table class="cover-detail">
          <caption>Diagnosis <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary floated small floated--always" onclick="window.location.href = '/cover-step2'" title="Go to the previous Add Cover page">Change</button></caption>
          
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>What have you been medically diagnosed with?</th>
              <td>lumbar spondylosis</td>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <th>Approximately when did the injury or disease happen (date of onset)?</th>
              <td>12 / 12 / 2005</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>What is the current status of your injury/condition?</th>
              <td><ul>
              	<li>permanent</li>
              	<li>stable</li>
              </ul></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>What is the ongoing effect of your injury/condition?</th>
              <td>none</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>Upload your GP or Specialist's medical report that includes your diagnosis (required) along with any supporting medical documentation.</th>
              <td><a href="#">Test image (114 KB JPG)</a></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <table class="cover-detail">
          <caption>Statement and supporting documents <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary floated small floated--always" onclick="window.location.href = '/cover-step3'" title="Go to the previous Add Cover page">Change</button></caption>          
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Which statement below best describes how your injury or disease happened?</th>
              <td>
                <ul>
                  <li>lifting loads of at least 25 kilograms while bearing weight through the lumbar spine to a cumulative total of at least 120 000 kilograms within any ten year period before the clinical onset of lumbar spondylosis</li>
                  <li>carrying loads of at least 25 kilograms while bearing weight through the lumbar spine to a cumulative total of at least 3 800 hours within any ten year period before the clinical onset of lumbar spondylosis</li>
                </ul>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <th>Based on this statement, how did your service cause or contribute to your injury or disease?</th>
              <td>hi this is my story</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>Upload any supporting documents that show how your service caused or contributed to your injury or disease.</th>
              <td><a href="#">Test image (114 KB JPG)</a></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <table class="cover-detail">
          <caption>How have you been affected by your condition? <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary floated small floated--always" onclick="window.location.href = '/cover-step4'" title="Go to the previous Add Cover page">Change</button></caption>          
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>As a result of my injury/condition, I require..</th>
              <td>
                <ul>
                  <li>medical treatment.</li>
                  <li>transport to/from medical appointments.</li>
                  <li>modifications to my home or vehicle</li>
                  <li>something not listed above.</li>
                </ul>
              </td>
            </tr>
		  </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <th>My injury/condition meant I was impacted financially by...</th>
              <td>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>I am interested in...</th>
              <td>
                <ul>
                  <li>getting a new job.</li>
                  <li>work experience.</li>
                </ul>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>My injury/condition has impacted my...</th>
              <td>
                <ul>
                  <li>ability to interact in social situations (Eg. interacting with friends and family).</li> 
                </ul>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <br><h3>By clicking submit, I acknowledge that the information that I have provided is truthful and accurate.</h3><br><br>
        <% include ../partials/waiting-bar.ejs %>
		<div class="pagination">
			<button disabled class="uikit-btn" onclick="window.location.href = '/cover-step4'" title="Go to the previous Add Cover page">Previous</button>&nbsp;
     		<button disabled class="uikit-btn" onclick="window.location.href = '/auth'" title="Save and exit the request for cover process">Save and exit</button>&nbsp;
     		<button disabled class="uikit-btn" onclick="window.location.href = '#open-modal'" title="Cancel the request for cover">Cancel</button>&nbsp;
			<button disabled class="uikit-btn floated" onclick="window.location.href = '/cover-step6'" title="Go to the next Add Cover page">Submit request for cover</button>
		</div>

		<% include ../partials/removefile-modal.ejs %>
		<% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>



  <% include ../../../global/partials/footer.ejs %>

  <script src="/docs/js/jquery-effects.js"></script>
  <script src="/docs/js/main.js"></script>
  <script>
    document.getElementById("percentage").style.width = "90%";
  </script>
</body>
</html>
